OL,3,CJoey Barton found guilty of assaulting
OL,4,Cwife at their home
OL,6,FFormer footballer Joey Barton has been
OL,7,Ffound guilty of assaulting his wife
OL,8,Fand handed a 12-week suspended
OL,9,Fsentence at Westminster Magistrates'
OL,10,FCourt.
OL,12,FThe former QPR midfielder left Georgia
OL,13,FBarton, 38, with a lump on her
OL,14,Fforehead and a bleeding nose after the
OL,15,Fincident in their family home in Kew,
OL,16,Fsouth-west London, in June 2021.
