OL,3,CJoey Barton found guilty of assaulting
OL,4,Cwife at their home
OL,6,FThey had each been drinking alcohol
OL,7,Fwith two other couples while their
OL,8,Fchildren slept upstairs, before having
OL,9,Fa drunken row about a family matter,
OL,10,FWestminster Magistrates' Court
OL,11,Fpreviously heard.
OL,13,FBarton, 42, then grabbed his wife and
OL,14,Fpushed her to the ground before
OL,15,Fkicking her in the head.
OL,17,FMrs Barton had called police
OL,18,Fimmediately after the incident, saying
OL,19,Fher husband had "just hit me", but
OL,20,Flater sent a letter to prosecutors
OL,21,Fretracting her allegations.
