OL,3,CJoey Barton found guilty of assaulting
OL,4,Cwife at their home
OL,6,FAt the same court on Tuesday, chief
OL,7,Fmagistrate Paul Goldspring rejected
OL,8,FBarton's account of events as "vague"
OL,9,Fas he convicted him of a single charge
OL,10,Fof assault by beating after a two-day
OL,11,Ftrial.
OL,13,FProsecutor Helena Duong told the court
OL,14,FMrs Barton's 999 call to police on the
OL,15,Fnight of the incident was "compelling
OL,16,Fevidence" of the assault, as she had
OL,17,Fdescribed it in "clear terms".
OL,19,FMrs Barton was not as affected by
OL,20,Falcohol as both she and Barton had
OL,21,Fsuggested, the prosecutor said.
