OL,3,CJoey Barton found guilty of assaulting
OL,4,Cwife at their home
OL,6,FBarton was taken to a local police
OL,7,Fstation where he gave a no-comment
OL,8,Finterview.
OL,10,FSimon Csoka, defending Barton, said it
OL,11,Fwas not clear what the period of time
OL,12,Fwas between Mrs Barton receiving the
OL,13,Finjury and making the 999 call.
OL,15,FReferring to the lump sustained on her
OL,16,Fhead, he told the court: "There are a
OL,17,Fnumber of circumstances where the
OL,18,Finjury may have been sustained
OL,19,Faccidentally."
