OL,3,CJoey Barton found guilty of assaulting
OL,4,Cwife at their home
OL,6,FThe former footballer was due to face
OL,7,Ftrial at a magistrates' court in 2022
OL,8,Fbut the case was adjourned after Mrs
OL,9,FBarton sent a letter to prosecutors
OL,10,Fretracting her allegations.
OL,12,FIn the letter, she said her injuries
OL,13,Fhad been caused by accident when a
OL,14,Ffriend moved in to separate the pair.
OL,16,FThe couple are still married and
OL,17,Fliving together, the court heard.
